37
00:04:15,990 --> 00:04:17,150
<font color="yellow">Hello.</font>

38
00:04:17,950 --> 00:04:20,760
<font color="yellow">- Two bottles of beer, please.
- Okay.</font>

39
00:04:24,260 --> 00:04:26,590
<font color="yellow">Have you changed in the three years that I was away?</font>

40
00:04:26,590 --> 00:04:28,760
