<font color="yellow">What are you talking about?</font>

47
00:04:45,260 --> 00:04:46,290
<font color="yellow">What is this?</font>

48
00:04:48,260 --> 00:04:49,620
<font color="yellow">(VIEWERSHIP BY MINUTE)</font>

