56
00:05:08,490 --> 00:05:10,920
<font color="yellow">and takes full responsibility for the weather.</font>

57
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:13,720
<font color="yellow">If a weather forecaster isn't a weather specialist reporter,</font>

58
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:16,390
<font color="yellow">what is she? An announcer? Then why is she a part of the newsroom?</font>

59
00:05:49,020 --> 00:05:53,320
<font color="yellow">(COMPLAINER)</font>

60
00:05:54,990 --> 00:05:57,390
<font color="yellow">I was fired anyway. Who cares about a fan?</font>

61
00:06:10,750 --> 00:06:11,890
