66
00:06:24,050 --> 00:06:25,120
<font color="yellow">Look.</font>

67
00:06:25,950 --> 00:06:28,150
<font color="yellow">How many weather forecasters are you a fan of?</font>

68
00:06:28,420 --> 00:06:30,190
<font color="yellow">Which announcers are you a fan of?</font>

69
00:06:30,190 --> 00:06:32,650
<font color="yellow">Or are you a fan of every woman on TV?</font>

70
00:06:33,150 --> 00:06:35,520
<font color="yellow">- Is that wrong?
- Of course, it's wrong.</font>

71
00:06:39,190 --> 00:06:40,590
<font color="yellow">Isn't it wrong?</font>

72
00:06:42,350 --> 00:06:43,420
<font color="yellow">Is it okay?</font>

73
00:06:45,420 --> 00:06:46,620
