75
00:06:52,890 --> 00:06:56,290
<font color="yellow">Why are you arguing with me whether or not it's wrong?</font>

76
00:06:59,320 --> 00:07:00,320
<font color="yellow">You're right.</font>

77
00:07:01,090 --> 00:07:02,120
<font color="yellow">Please...</font>

78
00:07:04,320 --> 00:07:06,750
<font color="yellow">sponsor me with your clothes.</font>

79
00:07:10,420 --> 00:07:11,650
<font color="yellow">Forget it, if you don't want to.</font>

80
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:17,420
<font color="yellow">I'm a businessman,</font>

