- Yes.</font>

84
00:07:37,490 --> 00:07:38,690
<font color="yellow">A friend or girlfriend.</font>

85
00:07:43,750 --> 00:07:46,120
<font color="yellow">Then I'll just become a friend or girlfriend.</font>

86
00:07:49,320 --> 00:07:53,120
<font color="yellow">I guess you don't need any more friends or girlfriends, right?</font>

87
00:07:54,020 --> 00:07:55,090
<font color="yellow">Right.</font>

88
00:07:56,790 --> 00:07:58,090
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

89
