<font color="yellow">Because I...</font>

90
00:08:00,820 --> 00:08:02,990
<font color="yellow">always need friends and boyfriend.</font>

91
00:08:12,690 --> 00:08:16,550
<font color="yellow">You looked like you were passing by. You may go.</font>

92
00:08:21,890 --> 00:08:24,850
<font color="yellow">Will you be okay? You look like you drank a lot.</font>

93
00:08:24,850 --> 00:08:25,890
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

94
00:08:29,490 --> 00:08:30,790
<font color="yellow">You did well today.</font>

95
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:41,390
<font color="yellow">There's no way.</font>

96
00:08:59,520 --> 00:09:01,490
<font color="yellow">(INTENSIVE CARE UNIT)</font>

97
00:09:13,490 --> 00:09:15,420
<font color="yellow">She hasn't eaten all day.</font>

98
00:09:15,520 --> 00:09:17,090
<font color="yellow">What if she faints?</font>

99
00:09:17,090 --> 00:09:19,820
<font color="yellow">She isn't sleeping either. Her light is on all night.</font>

100
00:09:19,820 --> 00:09:21,950
<font color="yellow">She stands by her window, looking out like a ghost.</font>

101
00:09:26,220 --> 00:09:27,450
<font color="yellow">She's asleep.</font>

102
00:09:30,890 --> 00:09:31,950
<font color="yellow">Kids!</font>

103
00:09:32,590 --> 00:09:33,650
<font color="yellow">Let's go!</font>

104
00:09:34,020 --> 00:09:35,920
<font color="yellow">Hello everyone.</font>

105
00:09:36,750 --> 00:09:39,520
<font color="yellow">We will now begin Newsleader...</font>

106
00:09:39,620 --> 00:09:42,090
<font color="yellow">for the last Friday of the month.</font>

107
00:09:42,690 --> 00:09:44,120
<font color="yellow">The first item.</font>

108
00:09:44,620 --> 00:09:47,450
<font color="yellow">You don't know where Ppal Gang lives, do you?</font>

109
00:09:47,450 --> 00:09:50,390
<font color="yellow">With 8th party congress soon to be held, it has been confirmed...</font>

110
00:09:50,390 --> 00:09:54,090
<font color="yellow">that North Korea launched another missile last night.</font>

111
00:09:54,090 --> 00:09:55,150
<font color="yellow">Do you know?</font>

112
00:09:55,990 --> 00:09:58,050
<font color="yellow">Are you meeting her alone or something?</font>

113
00:09:58,050 --> 00:10:00,920
<font color="yellow">They fired two, but both failed,</font>

114
00:10:01,190 --> 00:10:02,890
<font color="yellow">hurting their image.</font>

115
00:10:02,890 --> 00:10:03,890
<font color="yellow">Are you?</font>

116
00:10:08,690 --> 00:10:10,590
<font color="yellow">When you married my husband,</font>

117
00:10:11,020 --> 00:10:14,290
<font color="yellow">you handed me an invitation yourself. Do you remember?</font>

118
00:10:15,190 --> 00:10:16,860
<font color="yellow">But how could the ex-wife...</font>

119
00:10:17,150 --> 00:10:18,250
<font color="yellow">come to the wedding?</font>

120
00:10:18,250 --> 00:10:19,650
<font color="yellow">I gave a gift, too.</font>

121
00:10:20,150 --> 00:10:22,920
<font color="yellow">I gave 10,000 dollars. Don't say you don't remember.</font>

122
00:10:22,920 --> 00:10:25,360
<font color="yellow">How frightened do you think I was, as the bride,</font>

123
00:10:25,360 --> 00:10:27,150
<font color="yellow">when my husband's ex-wife...</font>

124
00:10:27,150 --> 00:10:29,050
<font color="yellow">gave 10,000 dollars as a wedding gift?</font>

125
00:10:29,050 --> 00:10:31,520
<font color="yellow">Do you think I gave 10,000 dollars...</font>

126
00:10:31,520 --> 00:10:34,150
<font color="yellow">because I liked you or Lee Joong Shin...</font>

127
00:10:34,150 --> 00:10:35,590
<font color="yellow">who was getting married in six months?</font>

128
00:10:36,190 --> 00:10:39,820
<font color="yellow">It was so that you wouldn't be cheap toward my daughter, Ppal Gang.</font>

129
00:10:39,820 --> 00:10:42,450
<font color="yellow">You used that to buy yourself a designer bag instead, didn't you?</font>

130
00:10:42,450 --> 00:10:44,920
<font color="yellow">Yes. How did you know?</font>

131
00:10:44,920 --> 00:10:46,950
<font color="yellow">I used the gift money from a snake...</font>

132
00:10:46,950 --> 00:10:49,450
<font color="yellow">to buy a bag made of an eel and I still carry it.</font>

133
00:10:49,450 --> 00:10:51,360
<font color="yellow">- Stop pretending to be a mum...
- Also,</font>

134
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:52,750
<font color="yellow">I fed and clothed Ppal Gang...</font>

135
00:10:52,750 --> 00:10:56,250
<font color="yellow">worth much more than 10,000 dollars using my own money.</font>

136
00:10:56,590 --> 00:10:58,890
<font color="yellow">Who's the mum? The woman who gives money to the stepmum...</font>

137
00:10:58,890 --> 00:11:02,250
<font color="yellow">or me, who cooked her three meals a day plus dessert for years,</font>

138
00:11:02,250 --> 00:11:04,850
<font color="yellow">going grocery shopping and packing her lunch every day?</font>

139
00:11:04,850 --> 00:11:07,450
<font color="yellow">I can't wait any longer. I'm going to find her and raise her myself.</font>

140
00:11:07,450 --> 00:11:09,390
<font color="yellow">I even have a room for her at my place.</font>

141
00:11:09,390 --> 00:11:10,990
<font color="yellow">You've never cooked in your life.</font>

142
00:11:10,990 --> 00:11:13,450
<font color="yellow">Will you take in a high school senior and starve her to death?</font>

143
00:11:13,550 --> 00:11:15,490
<font color="yellow">- Get out.
- I'm leaving.</font>

144
00:11:18,050 --> 00:11:19,490
<font color="yellow">Relax your eyes.</font>

145
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:29,390
<font color="yellow">Hey!</font>

146
00:11:32,920 --> 00:11:34,020
<font color="yellow">Taxi.</font>

147
00:11:57,150 --> 00:11:58,150
<font color="yellow">Come on.</font>

148
00:11:59,390 --> 00:12:00,390
<font color="yellow">Gosh.</font>

149
00:12:13,290 --> 00:12:14,790
<font color="yellow">Taxi!</font>

150
00:12:15,820 --> 00:12:18,420
<font color="yellow">Hi. Shinwol 2-dong, please.</font>

151
00:12:18,790 --> 00:12:19,990
<font color="yellow">Driver...</font>

152
00:12:23,090 --> 00:12:26,350
<font color="yellow">Please go to the intersection at the entrance to Shinwol 2-dong.</font>

153
00:12:26,350 --> 00:12:27,990
<font color="yellow">All right, to Shinwol-dong.</font>

154
00:12:31,390 --> 00:12:34,090
<font color="yellow">It was so hard to catch a taxi today.</font>

155
00:12:35,090 --> 00:12:37,650
<font color="yellow">Do you think it's because it's a Friday?</font>

156
00:12:38,090 --> 00:12:40,190
<font color="yellow">If it weren't for you,</font>

157
00:12:40,190 --> 00:12:42,350
<font color="yellow">I'd have stayed on the curb all night.</font>

158
00:12:42,350 --> 00:12:44,490
<font color="yellow">I was there for over 30 minutes.</font>

159
00:12:44,590 --> 00:12:46,420
<font color="yellow">Thank you so much.</font>

160
00:12:49,690 --> 00:12:52,890
<font color="yellow">I suddenly feel the alcohol hitting me. This is killing me.</font>

161
00:12:58,790 --> 00:12:59,890
<font color="yellow">Excuse me.</font>

162
00:13:00,050 --> 00:13:03,550
<font color="yellow">I feel nauseous. Could you please drive carefully?</font>

163
00:13:03,790 --> 00:13:05,990
<font color="yellow">I might throw up.</font>

164
00:13:08,920 --> 00:13:09,950
<font color="yellow">Excuse me.</font>

165
00:13:10,150 --> 00:13:12,390
<font color="yellow">You don't want to get in an accident.</font>

166
00:13:12,390 --> 00:13:14,890
<font color="yellow">You'll end up on the news.</font>

167
00:13:16,520 --> 00:13:17,620
<font color="yellow">Please.</font>

168
00:13:18,490 --> 00:13:19,890
<font color="yellow">I'm really going to throw up.</font>

169
00:13:19,890 --> 00:13:20,890
<font color="yellow">Look.</font>

170
00:13:21,150 --> 00:13:24,850
<font color="yellow">If you throw up here, you have to pay a penalty of 150 dollars.</font>

171
00:13:25,520 --> 00:13:27,220
<font color="yellow">I have to clean the dirty car,</font>

172
00:13:27,250 --> 00:13:29,790
<font color="yellow">and I won't be able to work for a day because of the smell.</font>

173
00:13:29,820 --> 00:13:31,590
<font color="yellow">Especially on a Friday like today,</font>

174
00:13:31,790 --> 00:13:33,420
<font color="yellow">150 dollars isn't enough.</font>

175
00:13:33,420 --> 00:13:35,290
<font color="yellow">Why are you trying to scare me?</font>

176
00:13:35,790 --> 00:13:37,620
<font color="yellow">This isn't a taxi.</font>

177
00:13:46,650 --> 00:13:47,690
<font color="yellow">Why you...</font>

178
00:13:51,890 --> 00:13:53,550
<font color="yellow">Are you sobering up from the walk?</font>

179
00:13:54,620 --> 00:13:56,590
<font color="yellow">Did you get in my car knowing it wasn't a taxi?</font>

180
00:13:58,450 --> 00:14:02,920
<font color="yellow">You wouldn't have given me a ride if I asked you to take me home.</font>

181
00:14:07,190 --> 00:14:08,190
<font color="yellow">Mr Lee.</font>

182
00:14:09,920 --> 00:14:12,990
<font color="yellow">Why do you think men never offer to take me home...</font>

183
00:14:12,990 --> 00:14:14,720
<font color="yellow">before I ask them to?</font>

184
00:14:16,520 --> 00:14:19,820
<font color="yellow">I always have to ask them to be my friend or boyfriend.</font>

185
00:14:19,820 --> 00:14:22,050
<font color="yellow">Why is my life so pathetic?</font>

186
00:14:22,090 --> 00:14:23,820
<font color="yellow">Where do you live?</font>

187
00:14:24,090 --> 00:14:25,990
<font color="yellow">It's over there. We're almost there.</font>

188
00:14:27,190 --> 00:14:29,820
<font color="yellow">I don't know how to thank you.</font>

189
00:14:29,820 --> 00:14:32,250
<font color="yellow">I've never had a taxi driver walk me home.</font>

190
00:14:32,250 --> 00:14:34,890
<font color="yellow">You're lucky a taxi driver is walking you home.</font>

191
00:14:35,990 --> 00:14:39,350
<font color="yellow">Mr Lee. Aren't you going to ask whom I drank with?</font>

192
00:14:39,350 --> 00:14:40,450
<font color="yellow">No, I'm not curious.</font>

193
00:14:43,450 --> 00:14:46,820
<font color="yellow">You're never curious about anything about me.</font>

194
00:14:50,650 --> 00:14:53,090
<font color="yellow">What are you even wearing?</font>

195
00:14:53,290 --> 00:14:56,550
<font color="yellow">Gosh. I don't believe this.</font>

196
00:14:57,650 --> 00:14:58,650
<font color="yellow">Here.</font>

197
00:15:15,320 --> 00:15:16,990
<font color="yellow">I'll carry her. She's heavy.</font>

198
00:15:17,450 --> 00:15:19,050
<font color="yellow">Make sure to move our car...</font>

199
00:15:19,590 --> 00:15:21,490
<font color="yellow">if the cars in front of the restaurant pull out.</font>

200
00:15:21,490 --> 00:15:22,490
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

201
00:15:22,920 --> 00:15:23,920
<font color="yellow">Na Ri?</font>

202
00:15:28,820 --> 00:15:31,890
<font color="yellow">I've never seen her with a man.</font>

203
00:15:32,090 --> 00:15:34,390
<font color="yellow">What's that? Is she drunk?</font>

204
00:15:34,820 --> 00:15:37,450
<font color="yellow">Na Ri looked totally sexy when she was doing the weather today.</font>

205
00:15:37,450 --> 00:15:39,820
<font color="yellow">Don't talk like that about Na Ri.</font>

206
00:15:39,820 --> 00:15:41,420
<font color="yellow">Stop talking about her and let's go.</font>

207
00:15:42,190 --> 00:15:44,590
<font color="yellow">Hey. Are you out of your mind? Where are you going?</font>

208
00:15:44,590 --> 00:15:45,850
<font color="yellow">Leave them alone and let's go.</font>

209
00:15:45,850 --> 00:15:47,890
<font color="yellow">You carry Ppal Gang.</font>

